title: AS Saint-Louisienne
text: Association Sportive Saint-Louisienne, commonly known as AS Saint-Louisienne, or simply as ASSL, is a <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club from <a href="Saint-Louis%2C%20R%C3%A9union">Saint-Louis</a>, <a href="R%C3%A9union%20Island">Réunion Island</a>. The club plays their home matches at <a href="Stade%20Th%C3%A9ophile%20Hoarau">Stade Théophile Hoarau</a>, which has a maximum capacity of 2,500 people.
